<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1">
    <%= image_tag(@item.image_url, class: 'fancy-frame') %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4">
    <div class="text-center signage">
      <div class="item-title">
        <%= @item.title %>
      </div>
      <div class="artist-name">
        <%= @item.artist_name%>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="item-info text-center">
On view this week is a <%= @item.medium %> dated <%= @item.object_date %>. It's dimensions are <%= @item.dimensions %>. Credit line: <%= @item.credit_line %>, Accession number: <%= @item.accession_number %>.
</div>
<div class="text-center">
This site features one object per week from the <a href="http://www.brooklynmuseum.org">Brooklyn Museum</a> using <a href="http://www.brooklynmuseum.org/opencollection/api/">their API</a>. It is not direclty affiliated with the museum.
</div>